Jay Tavare https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jay_Tavare 0 Jay Tavare (born March 17, 1971) is an American film and television actor, voice-over artist, and writer, probably best known for his role as Vega in Street Fighter. He has also appeared in Adaptation, Pathfinder, and Bone Tomahawk, the television miniseries Into the West, and the video game Metal Gear Solid V: The Phantom Pain, and is a contributor to HuffPost.
